We geometrically engineer d=4 N=1 supersymmetric Yang-Mills theories byconsidering M theory on various Joyce orbifolds. We argue that thesuperpotential of these models is generated by fractional membrane instantons.The relation of this superpotential to membrane anomalies is also discussed.